Due to some discomfort , I contacted and made advance appointment (at least 2 weeks) to see the doctor. On 2 occasions, the clinic called me one day before the scheduled appt and postponed it, each time having to wait 2 weeks. Not everybody has the luxury to wait for so long just to get a consultation.
So unprofessional of the clinic.
Dr.liana is very experienced doctor .. I feel very much comfortable with her.. definitely recommend gynaecologist to all women's.. thank you for staff also..
